msgid "# Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B"
msgstr "# Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B is a 72-billion parameter reward model designed for "
"mathematical reasoning and evaluation. It is part of Alibaba Cloud's Qwen "
"2.5 series, specifically optimized for scoring and ranking mathematical "
"problem solutions. The model supports a maximum context window of 128K "
"tokens and delivers enhanced capabilities in mathematical computation, step-"
"by-step reasoning evaluation, and solution quality assessment."
msgstr ""
"Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B 是一个720亿参数的奖励模型，专为数学推理和评估而设计。它是阿里云Qwen "
"2.5系列的一部分，特别针对数学问题解决方案的评分和排序进行了优化。该模型支持最大128K "
"token的上下文窗口，并在数学计算、逐步推理评估和解决方案质量评估方面提供了增强的能力。"

msgid ""
"This document provides a detailed workflow for the complete deployment and "
"verification of the model, including supported features, environment "
"preparation, single-node deployment, functional verification, and "
"performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档提供了模型完整部署和验证的详细工作流程，包括支持特性、环境准备、单节点部署、功能验证和性能评估。"

msgid ""
"The `Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B` model is supported since `vllm-ascend:v0.9.0`."
msgstr "`Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B` 模型自 `vllm-ascend:v0.9.0` 版本起得到支持。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型的支持特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B` (BF16 version):\n"
"    - With CPU offloading: requires at least 1 Atlas 910B4 (32G × 1) card or higher\n"
"    - Without CPU offloading: requires at least 4 Atlas 910B4 (32G × 4) cards or higher\n"
"  [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B)"
msgstr ""
"- `Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B` (BF16版本)：\n"
"    - 启用CPU卸载：至少需要1张Atlas 910B4 (32G × 1) 或更高规格的卡\n"
"    - 不启用CPU卸载：至少需要4张Atlas 910B4 (32G × 4) 或更高规格的卡\n"
"  [下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weights to a local directory (e.g., "
"`./Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B/`) for quick access during deployment."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到本地目录（例如 `./Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B/`），以便在部署期间快速访问。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run `Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B` directly."
msgstr "您可以使用我们的官方Docker镜像直接运行 `Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B`。"

msgid ""
"These versions support multi-NPU deployment, allowing the model to utilize "
"all available NPU devices (e.g., 4 NPUs) for improved performance."
msgstr "这些版本支持多NPU部署，允许模型利用所有可用的NPU设备（例如4个NPU）以获得更好的性能。"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动Docker镜像，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-docker)。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B supports single-node single-card deployment on the 910B4"
" platform. Follow these steps to start the inference service:"
msgstr "Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B 支持在910B4平台上进行单节点单卡部署。请按照以下步骤启动推理服务："

msgid ""
"1. Prepare model weights: Ensure the downloaded model weights are stored in the `./Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B/` directory.\n"
"2. Create and execute the deployment script (save as `deploy.sh`):"
msgstr ""
"1. 准备模型权重：确保下载的模型权重存储在 `./Qwen2.5-Math-RM-72B/` 目录中。\n"
"2. 创建并执行部署脚本（保存为 `deploy.sh`）："

msgid ""
"The `--task reward` parameter is required to run the model in reward model "
"mode for scoring mathematical solutions."
msgstr "需要使用 `--task reward` 参数以奖励模型模式运行模型，用于对数学解决方案进行评分。"

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"After starting the service, verify functionality using a `curl` request:"
msgstr "启动服务后，使用 `curl` 请求验证功能："

msgid ""
"A valid response (e.g., `{\"reward_score\": 1.69}`) indicates successful "
"deployment."
msgstr "有效的响应（例如 `{\"reward_score\": 1.69}`）表示部署成功。"

msgid "### Batch Reward Scoring"
msgstr "### 批量奖励评分"

msgid "You can also score multiple responses for comparison:"
msgstr "您还可以对多个响应进行评分以进行比较："

